Uses of Package
com.soa.transport.http.deploy

  • Packages that use com.soa.transport.http.deploy 
    Package Description
    com.soa.transport.http.deploy.impl  
  • Classes in com.soa.transport.http.deploy used by com.soa.transport.http.deploy.impl 
    Class and Description
    FilterRegistration
    Instances of this interface can be published as OSGi services, which will result in any capable HTTP server registering the filter and activating it.
    ListenerRegistration
    Interface that allows a servlet event listener to be published into OSGi.
    ResourceRegistration
    Instances of this interface can be published as OSGi services, which will result in any capable HTTP server registering the resources and publishing them.
    ServletRegistration
    Instances of this interface can be published as OSGi services, which will result in any capable HTTP server registering the servlet and publishing it.
    WebAppRegistration
    This interface may be used to publish a set of Web resources as a single web application including all servlets, filters, event listeners and static resources.
